              <tr><td colspan="3">    <table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr><td width="200" valign="top"><b>A Scorpion Telson</b><br>
LORE ITEM NO DROP <br>
Skill: Piercing&nbsp;&nbsp;Atk Delay: 24<br>
DMG: 3<br>
Effect: Poison Bolt<br>
WT: 2.5&nbsp;&nbsp;Range: 40<br>
Class: WAR, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG, NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC<br>
Race: ALL</td>
    
    <td width="100" align="center" valign="top">
    <b>Item Icon</b><br>
    <img src="itemicons/pierce018.jpg"></td>

    <td width="150" valign="top">
    <b>Obtained From</b><br>
    Heartsting Scorpions<br>
Level 12</td>
    <td width="150" valign="top">
    <b>Additional Info</b><br>
    Type: Weapon, Piercing<br>
Damage Per Second: 2.92<br>
Zone(s): bonefield<br>
Date Added: 04/24/00<br>
Last Updated: 05/08/00<br>
</td></tr>
    </table>
    <br><br>
    <b>Description</b><br>
This item is dropped by the Heartsting Scorpions, found in the Field of Bone.  There are two different versions of this item, both dropped by the same mob.  They both are identical except for one small thing.  The rarer of the two comes with one charge of Poison Bolt.
<br><br>
<b>Player Comments</b> (total:5, showing:1-5) <a href="JavaScript:popComment('comment.php3?type=item&tid=1774')">add</a><br>
<a href="mailto:natep84@yahoo.com">Gohann</a> of the Fennin Ro server on May. 08, 2000 at 03:10pm said...<br>
This drops off of heartsting scorpions.  The scorpions drop 2 versions of the stinger, one is 3dmg 24dly wt 2.5 rng 40 without an effect, the other is same stats with the effect Poison Bolt, you have to right click the stinger to get  it to work.  WARNING this item is expendable, meaning it only has a one time proc, but these are common, i use them to fight yellows and reds when i solo with my warrior :).  Hope this helps!<br><br>
<a href="mailto:j_baouns@home.se">JHGBaouns</a> of the Bristlebane server on May. 07, 2000 at 08:44am said...<br>
I got one with the poison bolt on it, but I never seen any effect of it. Maybe you have to be a over a level to use the effect?<br><br>
<a href="mailto:ewmaster@hotmail.com">Janoeb</a> of the Prexus server on May. 04, 2000 at 12:57am said...<br>
FYI, Heartstrings are 12 as a LOW. They go up to 14 and are tough even fights. I also have never seen one of these with poison bolt on it. Maybe that's a rare drop and the effectless is normal, but I'm not sure<br><br>
<a href="mailto:skev@hotmail.com">Skev</a> of the Prexus server on Apr. 30, 2000 at 12:23am said...<br>
